{"tid":2316011,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（一人一個）史上最差嘅信用卡廣告","createTime":"2020-12-07T14:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T04:54:08.000Z","uid":51200,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b76faae2fc5ec99af93ee78381861b745ead862f","tid":2316011,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:11:42.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇到啲信用卡廣告<br />\n呢個都應該係我暫時人生中睇過<br />\n最冇內涵，意識最露骨嘅信用卡廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vkEGB8C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvkEGB8C.png&h=2cb39d1d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bTgNxGY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbTgNxGY.png&h=41535e84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個廣告鼓吹緊既係<br />\n男人為咗一份區區嘅禮物透支、分期、欠債，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而另一方面<br />\n就講緊女方儘管知道男方揹住咗筆街數<br />\n但依然會因為收到份貴價禮物而開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實邊班Marketing諗到呢個垃圾既宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先唔講利用左信用卡分期嘅概念，物化男女關係<br />\n仲定型埋一定要係男方送貴價聖誕禮物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我屌你宜家咩年代，<br />\n條女送唔得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為香港冇男權組織+呢個廣告入邊女性係處於優勢（收禮物）<br />\n所以好似冇乜人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果將廣告入邊既男女角色調返轉一定大把女權撚屌<br />\n就算係而家都可以屌個廣告物化女性，<br />\n話女人淨係識收禮物啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n信用卡宣揚消費其實大家都明<br />\n咁但係有必要利用呢啲一睇就會俾人屌嘅陳舊理由同藉口咩<br />\n<br />\n我真係見到呢個廣告都覺得唔太舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家仲有冇睇過其他垃圾信用卡廣告？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c6525ce8e2151544cc9de6fba227aca70077ee","tid":2316011,"uid":321977,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:13:52.000Z","msg":"渣打狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />服務差到嘔"},{"pid":"bcde9d35d92b1bf21fca2bd4ff8ba32d1a7de083","tid":2316011,"uid":51200,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:16:14.000Z","msg":"如果再露骨啲去講呢個廣告<br />\n其實即係<br />\n「喂喂喂，快啲碌爆你男朋友張卡啦。分期咪得囉，反正佢咁鍾意你冇所謂啦。hehe。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n究竟渣打marketing班撚樣喺度諗咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得直情可以放入去教科書度做反面教材<br />\n直情橫跨晒現代價值丶男女關係同消費主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94db570773df1c0704c7243b2878d2c40f22d82f","tid":2316011,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5c6525ce8e2151544cc9de6fba227aca70077ee","tid":2316011,"uid":321977,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:13:52.000Z","msg":"渣打狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />服務差到嘔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T14:17:05.000Z","msg":"講真，回贈幾吸引<br />\n但真係掃晒興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ba2d2963f17dffc057e9ec7834aa425fcb78dc","tid":2316011,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020